creator: eReleGo Digi Media Pvt Ltd
descriptionHtml:
"Welcome to Bunts' Sangha RNS Vidyaniketan"

Bunts' Sangha RNS Vidyaniketan made a humble beginning with its toddler's steps in 1991 as Ramakrishna Vidyaniketan and rechristened as Bunts Sangha RNS Vidyaniketan, is now fast sprinting and has made a remarkable Niche for itself in the field of education in the city of Bangalore.

The strength steadily growing with 4000+ students catering from KG to PUC classes with ICSE Curriculum for the school section and Affiliated with PU Board, Govt of Karnataka, is situated in Vijayanagar Bengaluru.

5 Unique pillars of schooling at RNS vidyaniketan

1. Academic Excellence
Institution has well qualified and experienced staffs who strive towards motivating students to excel in academics.

2. Personal Attention
Students are supported and guided at each and every step and given clarifications when required.

3. Holistic development
All round development with Value based education with Yoga, Value education and NIE classes are a part of the curriculum for the holistic development of the student.

4. Best – in – Class Infrastructure
Spacious, ventilated classrooms with Interactive smart boards, collaborated with NIIT for interactive classes.

5. Safe Campus
Well monitored campus with security personnel deployed round the clock with CCTV cameras installed in the classrooms as well as around the premises.

Through this mobile App we offer
App For All
To provide the power of technology in the hands of Parents, Teachers and School Admin.

Fees Management Simplified
This app provides a solution to schools to automate their fees scheduling

Exam Results
Managing the scheduling of exams, publishing results and printing report could be a time-consuming task.

Time-table
Module provides an easy way to publish your time-table and manage teacher arrangement/substitution for absent teachers.

Attendance and Leave
A complete solution to automate attendance taking, attendance reporting, leave application and attendance analytics.Optional RFID

Assignments / Home works
Snap a picture of the blackboard or a worksheet. Write down a reminder to share. Record a rhyme. Share a link.

Many more...

Start to use to know exciting features.

descriptionHtml:
"Welcome to Bunts' Sangha RNS Vidyaniketan"

Bunts' Sangha RNS Vidyaniketan made a humble beginning with its toddler's steps in 1991 as Ramakrishna Vidyaniketan and rechristened as Bunts Sangha RNS Vidyaniketan, is now fast sprinting and has made a remarkable Niche for itself in the field of education in the city of Bangalore.

The strength steadily growing with 4000+ students catering from KG to PUC classes with ICSE Curriculum for the school section and Affiliated with PU Board, Govt of Karnataka, is situated in Vijayanagar Bengaluru.

5 Unique pillars of schooling at RNS vidyaniketan

1. Academic Excellence
Institution has well qualified and experienced staffs who strive towards motivating students to excel in academics.

2. Personal Attention
Students are supported and guided at each and every step and given clarifications when required.

3. Holistic development
All round development with Value based education with Yoga, Value education and NIE classes are a part of the curriculum for the holistic development of the student.

4. Best – in – Class Infrastructure
Spacious, ventilated classrooms with Interactive smart boards, collaborated with NIIT for interactive classes.

5. Safe Campus
Well monitored campus with security personnel deployed round the clock with CCTV cameras installed in the classrooms as well as around the premises.

Through this mobile App we offer
App For All
To provide the power of technology in the hands of Parents, Teachers and School Admin.
